33:02.481 --> 33:04.438
<i>Hoyt v. Florida.</i>

33:04.858 --> 33:06.975
State the facts
please, Miss...

33:07.486 --> 33:08.727
Valentin.

33:09.154 --> 33:10.986
Gwendolyn Hoyt was a housewife

33:11.072 --> 33:12.984
and her husband
was this asshole.

33:13.366 --> 33:15.779
Can you recall the specifics?

33:15.994 --> 33:18.202
He cheated on her.
He choked her.

33:18.455 --> 33:20.538
He'd rip off her clothes
and threaten to kill her.

33:20.707 --> 33:22.790
So, in statutory terms,

33:22.876 --> 33:24.083
he was a real asshole.

33:26.129 --> 33:29.839
On the night in question,
Clarence told his wife

33:29.925 --> 33:32.668
that he'd met another woman
and he was leaving her.

33:32.886 --> 33:36.129
How did Hoyt respond,
Miss Burton?

33:36.556 --> 33:38.889
She smashed in his skull
with a baseball bat.

33:39.184 --> 33:42.018
Then called an ambulance
while he was dying.

33:42.938 --> 33:46.648
The jury convicted Hoyt
for second-degree murder.

33:47.442 --> 33:49.308
And that's where
our story begins.

33:49.986 --> 33:51.727
A great civil rights lawyer

33:51.821 --> 33:54.108
took up Hoyt's appeal.

33:54.407 --> 33:55.773
Dorothy...

33:57.410 --> 33:58.617
Kenyon.

34:00.914 --> 34:03.281
On what grounds, Miss Roemer?

34:03.792 --> 34:06.751
That Florida's juries
violated the U.S. Constitution

34:06.836 --> 34:08.196
'cause there were
only men on them.

34:08.463 --> 34:11.251
Kenyon said that
if there were women on it,

34:11.341 --> 34:14.300
Hoyt may have been convicted of a
lesser crime, like manslaughter.

34:14.386 --> 34:16.172
But that law
makes sense, though.

34:17.138 --> 34:19.972
Women can't take care of their kids
if they're on some sequestered jury.

34:20.058 --> 34:21.969
- Oh, is that so?
- What?

34:22.060 --> 34:24.222
- Men are the mammoth hunters.
- Oh, my God.

34:24.312 --> 34:25.456
You're never
getting laid again.

34:25.480 --> 34:27.080
What about women
who don't have children?

34:27.107 --> 34:28.226
Or they're out of the house?

34:28.275 --> 34:30.891
Let the man stay home
and take care of his children.

34:31.235 --> 34:34.070
Hey, don't take it out on me.
I'm not holding my fiancée back.

34:34.155 --> 34:35.440
She's got two jobs.

34:35.532 --> 34:39.196
