40:38.353 --> 40:39.872
- That's not fair and you know it.
- Then I want you to walk

40:39.896 --> 40:42.333
me home, Marty, so I can sit in my corner
and write a lesson plan to inspire

40:42.357 --> 40:44.001
- the next generation of students...
